Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=======story=======
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你扑到我怀里来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我回来了 你这家伙真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:36.46,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(174,890)}应有之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你从南美带回来的礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见嘛 你居然看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不看报纸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想费脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}…的强势太平洋高压所驱赶 将会有多处放晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的计划排得满满的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划？什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有份光坐着就能赚5000日元的兼职 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做？还是不做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去跟他们说你做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 在兼职的地方用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 这里是折木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志啊 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我刚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎？他在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎 里志打电话找你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎 之前借你的书看完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是看完了 希望你快点还我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天过去拿方便吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职收工之后可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职收工之后可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职？奉太郎你兼职？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发什么神经了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心血来潮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替老姐的熟人看管市民泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你姐姐啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说你怎么可能那么勤劳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出门了 先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我之后过去取笑你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你便 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你们是三个人一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我联系了她们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是可以看到珍稀动物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福 你说的就是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 工作的奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实话说 我好失望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 难得来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起玩个开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死盯着老子的女人看 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿别扯上我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 再游一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我要开球了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同学 二传
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿千你不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同学 要接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要滑了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换班 你可以休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃午饭怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是早点说 就能做更像样点的午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话你最好对奉太郎说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为奉太郎简直就是活生生的嫌麻烦集合体嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他突然勤劳起来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么能错过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 像这样大家聚在一起很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得不太相称呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不相称？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池和奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们太过分了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳装和折木也不相称嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 还有太阳和奉太郎也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海和折木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有夏天和奉太郎之类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不能这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 回泳池去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那就把垃圾收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把椅子归位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再去买一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…一般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将来的梦想会不会是成为游泳运动员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人里说不定会出现能拿金牌的选手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可说不准
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只取决于那个人是否是能成为那种人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别的人就可以成功 而普通人则不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学想成为特别的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正 我始终是个普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学是特别的 对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同学和摩耶花同学也很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我有关的人们 对我来说都是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的主观想法就算了 我指的是一般而言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主观不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必在意和周围相比是普通还是特别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得只要有一个人觉得自己是特别的就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.98,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}白露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.98,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}阴气渐重 露凝而白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主观不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 换班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是奉太郎份内的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认得那位穿红色泳装的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚吃完饭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的左耳上戴着个白色的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 现在已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事真亏你能注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 注意到这个纯粹是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 这又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一那个是耳环怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人踩到了 搞不好是要受伤的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学 能和我们一起找找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么大的地方找…没开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定耳朵上戴着东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在找之前应该先向本人确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想这么做 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不太方便问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是要问什么奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你去问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 你是监视员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 之前发火的那个人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 我不想把事情闹大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就悄悄地找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我一个人办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我让其他人来监视 你就到泳池边巡逻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 泳池里就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然也会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 该怎么找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是分区负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你 拿出点干劲来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 这简直就像是白拿薪水的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少决定一下分工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦 我来想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 台阶那边就由千反田同学和摩耶花负责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑梯那边奉太郎来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳台就归我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份兼职是非做不可的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 你没想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的座右铭还真是随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太随便对不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总得有点反应啊 就算是牢骚也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则很无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我走了 回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是捡到弹珠拿来扔掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 看到现在的你就让人泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说 你很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就别看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的你看了就让人烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然都很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过至少做回之前的你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能互相较劲还更好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还更好一点…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不过或许不找也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 奉太郎你知道些什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田 你看到的真的是耳环吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是非常清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 她的左耳确实有个白色的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一边有的话 说不定是耳饰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我要问的并不是饰品的种类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是她耳朵上的究竟是不是饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看看她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果耳朵上戴着东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会这么随便地拍耳朵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是在她本人无意识的情况下附着上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样 那附上去的东西又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个…里志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把伊原抱起来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 在这种地方抱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那让千反田抱怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能因为是阿千就可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像小孩子一样 羞死人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想试试装成小孩子的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 为什么要做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了验证我的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指这件事的假设？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦 我做成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同学力气挺大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是按一般看法来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般会放在肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我可以下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我看到那位女性抱着那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们大概是母子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那孩子拿着冰淇淋被抱起来了会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 冰淇淋正好可能会沾到左耳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 现在它不见了是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳的时候掉了 或者是有人告诉了她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学的这一点 我还是觉得很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你夸我也不会有好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得久违了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎的挖苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见啊 你不挖苦我还要乱套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我还没道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹出这么大动静 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿千 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我说那是耳环的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那——么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一放下心来就觉得肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰淇淋怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 冰菓！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前说冰菓的原稿这次绝对会在明天给我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么说 应该说大致上好了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是还没写好吧 是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也 也可以这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只能这么说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福 现在马上回去写稿子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我一定要盯着你直到写完为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 哎呀 就差最后一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人也可以搞定的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿千 折木 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能写完就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢 被人需要是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿他能好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人需要…我今天也依靠了折木同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是吗 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道白色的东西就是冰淇淋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里没有其他白色的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 倒是还有一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那我也告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职 还请你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换班了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
